Class StaffWorker

java.lang.Object
foms.workers.Worker
foms.workers.StaffWorker
All Implemented Interfaces:

public class StaffWorker extends Worker implements Serializable
The `StaffWorker` class represents a staff worker in the food order management system. It extends the `Worker` class and implements the `Serializable` interface.
